  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个订单系统的ER图。核心实体有三个：客户（CUSTOMER）、订单（ORDER），还有订单里具体的行项目（LINE-ITEM）。客户可以下多个订单，但一个订单只属于一个客户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "ORDER",
        "LINE-ITEM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，CUSTOMER到ORDER是一对多关系。那ORDER和LINE-ITEM呢？是一个订单包含多个行项目吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ORDER",
        "LINE-ITEM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，一个订单必须包含至少一个行项目，而且每个行项目只能属于一个订单。这个关系用\"contains\"来描述。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ORDER",
        "LINE-ITEM",
        "contains"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把CUSTOMER和ORDER用\"places\"连起来了，一对多；ORDER到LINE-ITEM也是一对多，标注\"contains\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "ORDER",
        "LINE-ITEM",
        "places",
        "contains"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个实体差点忘了——送货地址（DELIVERY-ADDRESS）。一个客户可以有多个地址，一个地址也可能被多个客户共用，比如公司地址。这个关系比较灵活，用虚线表示非强制的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，CUSTOMER到DELIVERY-ADDRESS是多对多，关系名用\"uses\"，而且两边都不是强制的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个意思。另外整个图的标题就叫\"Order example\"吧，简洁明了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。四个实体、三个关系全部画好，标题也加上了。您看看还有什么需要调整的吗？",
